name: Corpo Seco
description: The Corpo Seco is a cursed being, a kind of undead that is doomed to roam the Earth terrorizing people. He is a corpse that was returned by the earth, which does not accept him because of the evils he did in life. The evils of the deceased who are transformed into a dry body are so great that neither God nor the devil wanted to receive his soul. His only action, according to legends, is to terrify those who see him. <Crypto Legends | A Series by Renancio Monte | 2021>
